cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper discusses techniques for reducing gradient estimation errors in the presence of observable input noise applied to the control signal, which is a common problem in reinforcement learning and motor control learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
